hadiths[43]{hadithnumber,text}:
2885,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin al-Aas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ilm teen chizon ka naam hai, aur jo unke ilawa hai wo izafi hai) buniyaadi nahin) mohkam aayaat , Sabit shuda sunnatein aur maali huqooq jo adl par mabni hon. ''"
2886,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main bimar ho gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) pedal chaltey huey meri iyaadat ke liye tashrif laye jabke mujh par be hoshiyari thi. mein aap se baat na kar saka, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wuzu kya aur wo pani mujh par dala to mujhey ifaaqa ho gaya. pas maine arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool! main apney maal mein kaisey karun jabkey meri waris meri behnein hain? to ( ye ( aayate-meeras nazil hui : ( يستفتونك قل الله يفتيكم في الكلالة . ... .) ''ye log aap se fatwa poochhtey hain, keh deejiye : Allah taala tumhen kalala ke baarey mein irshad farmata hai. ... . .''"
2887,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke main bimar ho gaya aur meri saat behney thin . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye, aapney merey chehrey par phunk maari to mujhey ifaaqa ho gaya aur maine arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya main apni behnon ke liye tihai maal ki wasiyat na kar jaun? aapney farmaya : '' ehsan kar .'' maine kaha : aadha maal ? aapney farmaya : '' ehsan kar .'' phir aap tashrif ley gaey aur mujhey chhod diya aur farmaya : ''aey Jabir ! main nahin samajhta ke tum us bimari se wafat paogey, Allah taala ne wahi nazil ki hai aur teri behnon ka haq bayan farma diya hai, un ke liye do tihai khas kya hai. '' to Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they ke aayat kareema : ( يستفتونك قل الله يفتيكم في الكلالة . ... .) merey hi baarey mein nazil hui thi."
2888,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, wo kehtey hain : aakhiri aayat jo nazil hui kalala ke baarey mein hai. ( يستفتونك قل الله يفتيكم في الكلالة . ... .) ."
2889,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! log aap sey, kalala ke baarey mein fatwa chahtey hain, to is '' kalala '' se kya murad hai? aapney (us ki tauzeeh mein) farmaya : '' tujhey wo aayat kafi hai jo garmi ke mausam mein nazil hui hai.'' (raawi abu-Bakar kehtey hain) maine abu-Is-haaq se kaha : ( kya kalala wo nahin ke) jo faut ho jaey aur na aulad chhod jaey aur na walid? unhoney kaha : ulama aisey hi kehtey hain."
2890,"Huzail bin Sharjeel Awdi se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari aur Salman bin Rabeea (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke paas aaya aur un se puchha ke eik shakhs faut hua, eik beti, eik poti aur eik haqeeqi behan chhod gaya. (uski meeras kis tarah taqseem ho?) un dono ne kaha : beti ke liye aadha hai aur sagi behan ke liye bhi aadha. poti ko unhoney mehroom thehraya. aur (kaha ke) Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas chaley jao (aur un se bhi poochh lo) wo hamari tasdeeq w taeed karengey. chunanche wo aadmi unke paas gaya aur mazkura masla puchha aur Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari aur Hazrat Salman bin Rabeea (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka jawab bhi bataya . to Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ( agar main bhi yehi jawab dun ( tab to main gumrah ho gaya aur hidayat yafta logon mein se na hua , main wo faisla deta hun jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne diya tha ke uski beti ke liye aadha aur poti ke liye eik hissey ( chata hissey ( hai do tihai ki takmil ke liye aur baqi maanda ( eik tihai ( wo haqeeqi behan ke liye hai."
2891,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, wo bayan kartey hain : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath nikley yahan tak ke eik Ansari aurat ke yahan pahunchey jo maqam Aswaaf (hudude-Haram Madina ( mein rihaaish pazeer thi , to ye aurat apni do betiyon ko lekar aai aur usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye Sabit bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ki betiyan hain jo aap ke sath mein they aur Uhud mein Shahid huey. unke chacha ne unka sara maal aur sari virasat le li hai aur unke liye koi maal nahin chhoda yahan tak ke sab par qabza kar liya hai. aey Allah ke Rasool ! aap kya farmatey hain? Allah ki qasam ! (is tarah to) unka kabhi nikah nahin hoga jab tak ke unke paas kuch maal na ho. pas Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah us mein faisla farma dega.'' aur phir Sura Nisa ki aayat : ( يوصيكم الله في أولادكم .... ( nazil hui. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aurat ko aur uskey dewar ko merey paas bulao.'' to aapney ladkiyon ke chacha se kaha : un dono ladkiyon ki do tihai aur unki maa ko aathwan hissey dey do aur baqi tumhara hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : is riwayat mein Bishr (bin Mufazzal ( ne ghalati ki hai. ye ladkiyan Saad bin Rabeea (Raziallahu anhu) ki betiyan thin . jabkey Sabit bin Qais ki shahadat Yamama ke moqe par hui hai."
2892,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Saad bin Rabeea (Raziallahu anhu) ki bewa ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! Saad Shahid ho gaey hain aur do betiyan chhod gaey hain. aur mazkura baala ki manind riwayat kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ye riwayat ziyada sahih hai.
2893,Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ne eik behan aur eik beti ko maiyat ka waris banaya aur her eik ko aadha aadha diya jabkey Hazrat Muaz un dino Yamen mein they aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) zinda they.
2894,"Hazrat Qabisa bin Zuweb (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik ( maiyat ki) ''nani'' Hazrat abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aai , wo apna haq virasat talab kar rahi thi. abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki kitab mein tera koi hissey ( mazkur ( nahin hai aur na mujhey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat se kuch maloom hai. tum lot jao yahan tak ke main logon se poochh lun . chunanche unhoney logon ( Sahaba ( se puchha to Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan hazir tha to aapney usey ( nani ko) chhata hissey diya tha. abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha : kya us khabar ke silsiley mein tumharey sath koi aur bhi hai? to Muhammad bin Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) uthey aur unhoney usi tarah kaha jaisey ke Mughira-bin-Shoba ne kaha tha. chunanche Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne nani ko ye hissey diya. phir eik aur '' daadi '' Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aai , wo apna haq virasat talab kar rahi thi. unhoney kaha : Allah ki kitab mein tumhara koi haq (mazkura ( nahin. aur jo faisla us se pehley hua hai wo dusri ( nani (ke liye tha aur main huqooq virasat mein kuch nahin badha sakta lekin wo chata hissey hi hai. agar tum dono ( nani aur daadi ( jama ho jao to ye hissey tum dono ke beech hoga. aur jo tum mein se koi akeli ho ( daadi ho, nani na ho, ya nani ho, daadi na ho ( to ye chata hissey purey ka pura ley gi ."
2895,Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne daadi ya nani ke liye chhata hissey muqarrar kya tha. lekin jab us se pehley (warey) maa na ho.
2896,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur usney kaha : mera pota faut ho gaya hai, to merey liye uski virasat mein se kya hai? aapney farmaya : '' terey liye chhata hissey hai. '' jab usney pusht pheri to aapney usey bulaya aur farmaya : '' terey liye eik aur chata hissey bhi hai. '' jab usney pusht pheri to aapney usey bulaya aur farmaya : ''ye doosra chhata hissey tohfa hai. Qatada (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : log nahin jaan sakey ke kis chiz ke sath usey waris banaya. Qatada ne (ye bhi) kaha : dada ka kam se kam hissey virasat chhata hai."
2897,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha tum mein se koi janta hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dada ko kya virasat di thi? to Hazrat Maaqil bin Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main janta hun, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey chhata hissey diya tha. unhoney puchha : kis ke sath? kaha : mujhey nahin maloom. to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : tum ne nahin jana ( tumhara adhuri baat bataaney ka ( kya faeeda?"
2898,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jin logon ke hissey muqarrar hain, unke darmiyan maal ko usi tarah taqseem karo jaisey kitabullah main hai, aur un se jo bach rahey to wo qarib tareen mard ka haq hai. ''"
2899,"Hazrat Miqdam (bin Maadikarb ( (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo koi qarza ya baal-bachchey chhod gaya to wo merey zimmey hain. ... . aur kabhi yun bhi farmaya. ... . ke Allah aur uskey Rasool ke zimmey hain. aur jo koi maal chhod jaey to wo uskey warison ke liye hai. aur jiska koi waris na ho main uska waris hun, uski taraf se diyat ada karunga aur uska waris banunga, aur mamu uska waris hai jis ka koi aur waris na ho, wo uski taraf se diyat ada kerega aur uska waris bhi banega.''"
2900,"Hazrat Miqdam (bin Maadikarb) Kandi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main her momin ke liye uski apni zaat se bhi qarib tar hun, jo shakhs qarz ya chhoti aulad chhod jaey to wo merey zimmey hai aur jo koi maal chhod jaey to wo uskey warison ka hai, main uska wali hun jis ka koi wali na ho, mein uskey maal ka waris banunga aur uskey qaidi chhudaaunga. aur mamu uska waris hai jiska aur koi waris na ho, wo uskey maal ka waris hoga aur uska qaidi chhudaaeyga. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ( الضيعة (ke maani hain ayaal. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : us riwayat ko zubaidi ne  (عن راشد بن سعد عن  ابن عائذ  عن مقدام) ki sanad se riwayat kya. aur Muawiya bin Saleh ne b-waasta Rashid usey riwayat kya to ( an (an) (ke bajaey ( ) سمعت المقدام ( yani maine Miqdam se suna hai, kaha ."
2901,"saleh bin Yahya bin Miqdam apney walid se wo dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''main uska waris hun jis ka koi waris na ho, mein uska qaidi chhudaunga aur uskey maal ka waris banunga . aur mamu uska waris hai jiska koi waris na ho, wo uska qaidi chhudaaeyga aur uskey maal ka waris banega.''"
2902,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka eik ghulam faut ho gaya aur kuch maal chhod gaya , uski koi aulad aur koi rishte daar na tha. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' uski virasat uski basti walon mein se kisi ko dey do.'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : Sufiyan (Rahimahullah) ki riwayat zyada kamil hai. aur Musaddad ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne daryaft farmaya : ''kya yahan koi uskey ilaqey ka rehney wala hai? '' Sahaba ne kaha : ji haan . aapney farmaya : '' uski virasat usi ko dey do .''"
2903,Janab Abdullah bin Barida apney walid se riwayat kartey hain kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas eik aadmi aaya aur usney kaha : merey paas qabeela Azd ke eik aadmi ki meeras hai aur mujhey koi azdi nahin mila ke usey de-dun . aapney farmaya : '' jao eik saal tak talash kartey raho ke koi qabeela Azd se mil jaey.'' chunanche wo eik saal ke baad aaya aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey koi azdi nahin mila ke uskey hawaley kar dun . aapney farmaya : '' jao aur bano khuza-aa ka jo aadmi tumhen sab se pehley miley ye uskey hawaley kar do .'' jab usney peeth pheri to aapney farmaya : '' us aadmi ko merey paas lao .'' jab wo aaya to aapney farmaya : '' khuza-aa ka bada aadmi dekho yani jo us badey se qarib tar ho. to ye meeras uskey hawaley kar do.''
2904,Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke bano khuza-aa ka eik aadmi faut ho gaya to uski meeras Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas laee gaee . aapney farmaya : '' uska koi waris ya zi-reham talluq daar talash karo.'' magar koi waris ya zi-reham talluq daar na mila. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye maal bano khuza-aa ke badey ko de-do yani jo qabeele ke sabsey badey se qarib tar ho.'' Yahya bin Adam kehtey hain : maine shareek se is hadees main eik baar yun suna : '' bano khuza-aa ke sab se badi umr waley ko dekho .''
2905,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik shakhs faut ho gaya. uska koi waris na tha siwaye eik ghulam ke jis ko usney azad kya tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne daryaft farmaya : ''kya uska koi waris hai? '' logon ne kaha : nahin, siwaye eik azad karda ghulam ke . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski virasat usi ko dey di."
2906,"Hazrat Waasila bin Isqaa (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : '' aurat teen tarah ki virasat jama kar leti hai : apney ghulam ki, us bachey ki jo usey kahen se gira-pada mil gaya ho aur us bachey ki jiskey baarey mein usney ( apney shohar sey) liaan kya ho.''"
2907,Janab Mak-hool (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne liaan wali aurat ke bachey ki meeras uski maa ke liye makhsus ki thi aur baad Azan us aurat ke warison ke liye hogi .
2908,"Amr bin Shuaib ne apney walid sey, unhoney apney dada sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se isi ki manind riwayat ki ."
2909,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''musalman kisi kafir ka ya koi kafir musalman ka waris nahin ho sakta.''"
2910,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke maine Hajjatil-wadaa ke moqe par arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aap kal kahan utrengey? aapney farmaya : ''kya Aqeel ne hamarey liye koi makaan chhoda bhi hai? '' phir farmaya : '' ham khaif bani kinaana mein padaaw karengey jahan Quraish ne kufr par qasmen uthai thin .'' aap ki murad wadi mohssab thi aur Qureshiyon ne us jagah bano Hashim ke khilaf qasmen khai thin ke na un se rishta-naata karengey, na kuch khareedein-bechengey aur na unhen panah dengey . Zohri (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain, ( kheef ( '' wadi ka naam hai."
2911,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' do mukhtalif millaton (aur deeno ( waley eik doosrey ke waris nahin bantey.''"
2912,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Barida (Raziallahu Anhuma) ki riwayat hai ke eik yahudi aur eik musalman do bhai they. wo apna jhagda Yahya bin Yamar (Rahimahullah) ke yahan lekar aaye to unhoney musalman ko waris qarar diya aur kaha ke mujhey abul-Aswad (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kya, usko eik aadmi ne bayan kya ke Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna hai : ''Islam badhta hai kam nahin hota.'' aur musalman ko waris qarar diya."
2913,abul-Aswad deli (Rahimahullah) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas eik yahudi ki meeras laee gaee jiska waris musalman tha. aur mazkura hadees ke ham-maani Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kya.
2914,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo taqseem (qabl az Islam) jahiliyat mein ho chuki so ho chuki (wo usi ke mutabiq rahegi) aur jo Islam qubul kerney tak nahin hui, wo ab Islam ke dastoor ke mutabiq hogi.''"
2915,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne irada kya ke eik londi kharida kar azad kar den, to londi ke malikon ne kaha : ham ye aap ko farokht kar detey hain, lekin uska wala hamarey liye rahega, (us ki wafat par uska maal ham lengey ya nisbate-wala ham se mutalliq rahegi.) Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne unki ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se zikr ki, to aapney farmaya : '' (unki ye baat ( terey liye koi maane (rukawat) nahin hai, kyonkey wala usi ka hota hai jo azad karey. ''"
2916,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wala usi ka haq hai jo qeemat ada karey aur ehsan karey.'' ( azadi dilaaey .)
2917,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Rimab bin Huzefa ne eik aurat se shaadi ki, to us se unke teen ladkey paida huye, phir unki maa faut ho gaee to wo bachey apni maa ke gharon aur ghulamon ke wala ke waris huey. Hazrat Amr bin al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) un bachon ke usba they. (yani waris they) wo unhen shaam ley gaey jo wahan ja kar faut ho gaey. (ye bachey taaoon amwaas mein faut huey they) Hazrat Amr bin al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) wapis aaye jabkey us aurat ka eik ghulam bhi wafat pa gaya aur maal chhod gaya tha. to aurat ke bhaiyon ne Hazrat Amr bin al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se ( apni behan ke wala ke silsiley mein) jhagda kya aur maamla Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke samney pesh kya. to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : '' bete ne ya baap ne jo bhi jama kya ho wo uskey ( usba (ka hota hai jo bhi hon.'' chunanche unhoney (us faisley ki) eik tehreer likhi jismein Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu), Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) aur eik aur aadmi ki gawahi sabt ki. phir jab Abdul-Malik khalifa huey to aurat ke bhaiyon ne ye muqadma Hisham bin Ismael ya Ismael bin Hisham ke samney pesh kya. usney unko Abdul-Malik ke yahan bhej diya. to Abdul-Malik ne kaha : ye wohi faisla hai jo mera khayal hai ke main pehley dekh chuka hun. chunanche usney Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ki tehreer ke mutabiq hamarey haq mein faisla kar diya aur ab tak ham usi mein hain. ( ب ( Humaid ne kaha : is hadees ki baabat log Amr bin Shuaib ko muttahim kartey hain. Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Hazrat abu-Bakar , Hazrat umr aur Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) se us (mazkura ( hadees ke khilaf riwayat hai lekin Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se uskey misl riwyayat hai."
2918,"Hazrat Tameem daari (Raziallahu anhu) ne sawal kya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! jab koi shakhs kisi musalman ke haath par Islam qubul karta hai to us baarey mein mashroo sunnat kya hai? aapney farmaya : ''zindagi aur maut mein wohi sab se badh kar uska wali hai.'' (uskey sath neki, eisaar aur ehsan ka maamla karta rahey.)"
2919,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne nisbat wala ko bechney ya kisi ko hiba kar deney se mana farmaya hai.
2920,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' (naya paida hua) bacha jab aawaz buland karey to waris hoga.''
2921,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne aayate-kareema : ( والذين عاقدت أيمانكم فآتوهم نصيبهم . . . . .) ki tafseer mein bayan kya ke eik aadmi doosrey ka haleef bin jata tha jabkey un mein koi nasbi qurbat na hoti thi phir her eik doosrey ka waris bhi hota tha, to is hukm ko sura Anfal ne mansookh kar diya. Allah taala ne farmaya : ( وأولو الأرحام بعضهم أولى ببعض . ... ( '' rishtey natey waley eik doosrey se ziyada nazdik hain. ''"
2922,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke aayat kareema ( والذين عاقدت أيمانكم فآتوهم نصيبهم . . . .) ki tafseer mein farmaya ke muhajrin jab Madina aaye to ansaar ke waris wohi ( muhajrin ( bantey they na ke deegar rishta daar . ye is bina par tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unke aapas mein bhai chaara qaaim farma diya tha. phir jab ye aayat utri : (ولكل جعلنا موالي مما ترك . ۔) to usney ( والذين عاقدت أيمانكم فآتوهم نصيبهم ( ko mansookh kar diya. magar aam nusrat , khair khuwahi aur taawun ko qaaim rakha. wo eik doosrey ko wasiyat bhi kar saktey they, jabke virasat khatam kar di gaee."
2923,"Janab Dawud bin Husain bayan kartey hain ke main Umme- Saad bint Rabeea ke yahan padha karta tha jabke wo yateem thin aur Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki zer tarbiyat thin , to maine yun qirat ki) والذين عاقدت أيمانكم ( usney kaha : ( والذين عاقدت أيمانكم ( mat padho .) balke baat ye hai ke) ye aayat Hazrat abu-Bakar aur unke bete Abdur-Rehman ke silsiley mein nazil hui thi , jabkey usney Islam qubul kerney se inkar kar diya tha. to Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne qasam khai thi ke usey apni virasat nahin dunga. phir jab usney Islam qubul kar liya to Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko hukm diya ke wo usey uska hissey den . Abdul-Azeez (bin Yahya ( ne mazeed kaha : Abdur-Rehman ne us waqt tak Islam qubul nahin kya jab tak ke usey talwaar ke zor par majboor nahin kar diya gaya. ( jab Islam bazor talwaar ghalib aa gaya aur bahut se log Islam laney par majboor ho gaey . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ( uqdat (ka mafhoom halaf yani qasam khaney ke maani mein hoga. ( Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne qasam khai thi ke apney ghair Muslim bete ko virasat nahin dengey .) aur jo ( عاقدت ( padhtey hain unke nazdik maani '' bahami (aapsi) ehad w paimaan '' hain. aur sabiqa hadees Talha bin Musrif ziyada sahih hai."
2924,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke unhoney aayate-kareema : ( والذين آمنوا وهاجروا . . . .) aur) والذين آمنوا ولم يهاجروا . . . .) ki tafseer mein farmaya ke dehati ( musalman jisney hijrat na ki hoti ( Muhajir ka waris na banta tha. phir us hukm ko aayat kareema : ( وأولو الأرحام بعضهم أولى ببعض . . . .) ne mansookh kar diya.
2925,"Hazrat Jubair bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Islam mein koi (naya) halaf nahin hai aur Islam se pehley (jahiliyat ke dinon mein) jo ehad muahidey ho chukey unko Islam ne aur mazboot kya hai.''"
2926,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamarey ehatey mein beth kar muhajrin aur ansaar ke darmiyan bhai-chaara qaaim farmaya tha. un se kaha gaya : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye nahin farmaya : ''Islam mein koi halaf nahin.'' to unhoney jawab diya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamarey ehatey mein beth kar muhajrin aur ansaar ke darmiyan halaf qaaim kya tha. unhoney apni ye baat do ya teen baar dohraai.
2927,Janab Saeed bin Musaiyab (Rahimahullah) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they : diyat kunbey walon ka haq hai) jo baap ki taraf se qurbat daar hotey hain. (aur aurat apney shohar ki diyat mein se kuch na paeygi yahan tak ke suhaak bin Sufiyan ne un se kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey likha tha ke main Ashim Zibabi ki biwi ko uskey shohar ki diyat se hissey dilaun. chunanche Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni raey se ruju kar liya . Ahmed bin Saleh ne bayan kya ke hamen ye hadees abdur-Razzaaq ne Zohri ke wastey aur unhoney Saeed se riwayat ki hai. aur us mein hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne suhaak ko dehatiyon par aamil banaya tha.
